--- .gitignore (原始)


+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Dependencies
venv/
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Logs
*.log

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/

# Coverage reports
.coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/

# Distribution / packaging
dist/
build/
*.egg-info/
```